metadata.name: Brainy Apes #1
metadata.description: BAS is a collection of 2,000 genetically enhanced laboratory apes. The apes have undergone significant genetic alterations. Their genes have been spliced, giving them amplified intelligence and enormous brains compared to typical apes. Ownership of a Brainy Ape grants members-only benefits including access to an elite society of ordinary people doing extraordinary things through blockchain innovations.
